            "title": "淡馬錫旗下富敦逐步關閉在中國大陸的對沖基金業務",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"淡馬錫旗下富敦逐步關閉在中國大陸的對沖基金業務\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6kzxGhJ2sJ_OwIkNWKjiGw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-02/91d07c30-c3c4-11ee-bdef-fe59cb899cb9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">淡馬錫旗下富敦逐步關閉在中國大陸的對沖基金業務</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B7%A1%E9%A6%AC%E9%8C%AB%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E5%AF%8C%E6%95%A6%E9%80%90%E6%AD%A5%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99-022713857.html",
