            "title": "聯儲局「潛在」新主席哈塞特預計下周會減息25個基點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"聯儲局「潛在」新主席哈塞特預計下周會減息25個基點\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6GdXP1te_lUqa7VyHkoUcQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/74158220-d179-11f0-afff-accf139ac47c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">聯儲局「潛在」新主席哈塞特預計下周會減息25個基點</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83-%E6%BD%9B%E5%9C%A8-%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E5%93%88%E5%A1%9E%E7%89%B9%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%83%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF25%E5%80%8B%E5%9F%BA%E9%BB%9E-231414611.html",
